<div class="container px-4">
  <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
      <p class="lead mb-3 green-link"> Is VerdGem Quiz free to use?</p>
      <p class="lead">
        <u>Yes!</u> VerdGem Quiz is completely free until June 30th, 2025. 
        We're offering this free trial period to help students preparing for their upcoming CSEC exams. 
        After June 30th, we'll introduce subscription tiers with both free and premium options.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
      <p class="lead mb-3 green-link"> How many quiz attempts can I take during the free trial? </p>
      <p class="lead">
        During the free trial period, each student
        account has a monthly limit of 30 quiz attempts. This allowance ensures you
        can thoroughly practice all subjects without limitations while we continue
        to build this platform.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
      <p class="lead mb-3 green-link"> Which CSEC subjects are covered by VerdGem Quiz? </p>
      <p class="lead">
        We currently cover the Information Technology subject. 
        We're continuously adding more subjects based on student demand. Each subject includes 
        comprehensive topic coverage aligned with the latest CSEC syllabus.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
      <p class="lead mb-3 green-link"> Can I focus on specific topics within a subject? </p>
      <p class="lead">
        <u>Absolutely!</u> You can choose to take quizzes on entire subjects or drill down to
        specific topics within each subject. This targeted approach helps you focus on areas
        where you need the most improvement.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
      <p class="lead mb-3 green-link"> Can I review my past quiz attempts? </p>
      <p class="lead">Yes, VerdGem maintains a complete history of all your quiz attempts. 
      You can review your previous answers, see the feedback provided, and track your 
      improvement over time through your personal dashboard.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
      <p class="lead mb-3 green-link"> How does VerdGem Quiz grade my answers? </p>
      <p class="lead">
        VerdGem uses AI technology to evaluate your answers. 
        The AI analyzes your responses against model answers, checking for key concepts 
        and correct application of CSEC curriculum points. This provides instant, personalized 
        feedback to help you improve your understanding of each topic.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= link_to "Back to Homepage", authenticated_root_path, class:"btn btn-dark btn-lg mt-4" %>
</div>
